  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This adversarial sample introduces W-AR-01: several CredibilityFactors declare a requiredLevel but omit the acceptanceCriteria field entirely, leaving the rationale for the required level undocumented. Decision is recorded as Accepted to stress-test weakener detection against a superficially passing package.",
